{"tid":352714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印航空公司推出單身女旅客座位安排","createTime":"2017-08-09T03:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T03:48:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6246d803ce287a9075f27272dd41d8281a552895","tid":352714,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:48:25.000Z","msg":"有鑑於收到唔少女仕係飛機上遇到性騷擾以及咸豬手，印度航空公司Vistara就係今個月正式推出女性飛行服務，減少女性受到影響，同時鼓勵女性即使隻身出遊都唔需要擔心。<br />\n<br />\n旅客係網上訂機票時，只要指明自己係獨自乘搭航機嘅女性，系統就會自動安排該乘客坐窗口位或者通道位置，而唔會按排俾其他乘客圍住兩邊嘅座位，一來方便佢地出入，二來亦可避免佢地受到騷擾嘅機會。此外，航空公司亦會幫女性乘客安排接駁交通工具好似的士時，都會幫旅客選擇，並留意該的士有無合法登記，同埋記低個架的士嘅車牌號碼，所有嘅措施都係希望旅客能夠比較放心同安心到印度旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tKCzj8XEaJEdBLVFC8USbw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/3b87bb7350eacf26be9371fbe8286610\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtKCzj8XEaJEdBLVFC8USbw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F3b87bb7350eacf26be9371fbe8286610&h=8804d999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ez4loOddoe9rKCguS3eofw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTIw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/0111fe61c1b049264a424fe5df5341ae\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fez4loOddoe9rKCguS3eofw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTIw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F0111fe61c1b049264a424fe5df5341ae&h=742aaf74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vs8ozmB2ZfG.xE8_kJR4_g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/e7317c509837e375002ddaabb3f2309b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.co